### Development environment setting
```bash
$ git clone ...
$ cd president-speech
$ pdm venv create
$ source .venv/bin/activate
$ pdm install
```

```bash
$ pdm add -dG test pytest pytest-cov
$ pdm test
$ pdm ptest

$ pdm ctest
---------- coverage: platform darwin, python 3.9.18-final-0 ----------
